{"tid":2231071,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【上岸】公開大學開辦物理治療學榮譽理學士","createTime":"2020-10-05T11:42:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T13:10:30.000Z","uid":225931,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a73de252574d4780e5e30300e16f5ce1b2100391","tid":2231071,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T11:42:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vImUbAa3KI4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvImUbAa3KI4&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=211beb3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vImUbAa3KI4</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人口老化問題持續，醫療人手普遍出現短缺，本港現有註冊物理治療師只有2,956名，以700萬香港人口計算，平均每1名物理治療師就要服務2,368名香港市民。根據《醫護人力規劃和專業發展策略檢討報告》指出，推算物理治療師在未來3年將有710人短缺，而到2030年更有933人短缺。修讀物理治療學畢業生，可入職二級物理治療師，起薪點14級，即港幣每月27,485元，頂薪點更可高達港幣每月44,415元，相對其他學系畢業生，收入已非常可觀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nJUPAS SSSDP: <a href=\"https://www.jupas.edu.hk/en/programme/sssdp/JSSU55/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jupas.edu.hk%2Fen%2Fprogramme%2Fsssdp%2FJSSU55%2F&d=SBcu0iNh8WN0EYdC3CIZL%2BoeOpwBOZOods3%2BbOb6780%3D&h=dab4c32e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.jupas.edu.hk/en/programme/sssdp/JSSU55/</a>"},{"pid":"4391ec7ae048e83d7c2fc777025c8baf406ac26e","tid":2231071,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T11:43:25.000Z","msg":"公大護理系屌打"},{"pid":"6d73148aae53deb453f105429d17925eb21922c5","tid":2231071,"uid":211323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T11:43:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e7975456ebec6e7bfebe22dd597aa5baef22c80","tid":223107